			<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
			Last night I went to talk with Mrysilla, whom I thought was the Gypsy in North Karana who sold the combine weapons.  She conned indifferent to me, so I walked up to talk with her.  She would reply with either &quot;Can't you see I am busy right now&quot; or &quot;I am closed right now&quot;.  Does she only speak to one customer at a time?  Is there a certain time of day to do business with her?  Is this even the right person to be speaking to?  Is there something I have done wrong?  I would have hung out all night if it were not for the frequent spawn of Grimfeather who flys right through the camp, and would wipe the floor with my paultry lv 9 Bard fanny.<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
Festivus<BR>
Bard of the ninth song<BR>
Erollisi Marr<BR>
