			When an NPC says he/she is too busy to deal with you, it means he/she was either recently attacked, or something else distracted them... don't bother waiting around, one time a NPC told me he was too busy, so I camped and went to sleep... 10 hours later I logged back on and he was still busy... probably an extreme case, since they normally recover in about 20 mins or so, but still something to note.
